---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout locale="en" title="Privacy - Nido's Gaming Stack" description="Privacy notes for Nido's Gaming Stack.">
  <section class="container-page section-space">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">Privacy</h1>
    <div class="mt-8 max-w-3xl space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-muted">
      <p>Nido's Gaming Stack is currently a static website. It does not use a database or account system.</p>
      <p>Download mirrors, feedback forms, analytics, or embedded media may be hosted by third-party services in future versions. When those services are added, this page should be updated with clear details.</p>
      <p>中文说明：本站当前为静态网站，不提供账号系统，不主动收集个人信息。后续如果接入反馈问卷、统计或第三方媒体服务，应在此页面补充说明。</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
